Name: ``bias``
Title: Mean Error
Abstract: Average signed prediction error indicating overestimation or underestimation

Name: ``count``
Title: Count
Abstract: Number of observations in the dataset

Name: ``mean``
Title: Mean
Abstract: Arithmetic mean of the sample or population values

Name: ``p05``
Title: 5th Percentile
Abstract: Value below which 5% of the observations fall

Name: ``p25``
Title: 25th Percentile
Abstract: Value below which 25% of the observations fall

Name: ``p50``
Title: 50th Percentile
Abstract: Value below which 50% of the observations fall

Name: ``p75``
Title: 75th Percentile
Abstract: Value below which 75% of the observations fall

Name: ``p95``
Title: 95th Percentile
Abstract: Value below which 95% of the observations fall

Name: ``px``
Title: Exceedance Probability
Abstract: Probability of a value being exceeded P(X>=x)

Name: ``r2``
Title: Coefficient of Determination
Abstract: Proportion of variance in the dependent variable explained by the model

Name: ``rmse``
Title: Root Mean Squared Error
Abstract: Square root of the average of squared prediction errors

Name: ``sd``
Title: Standard Deviation
Abstract: Square root of variance, representing spread in the same units as the data

Name: ``sum``
Title: Sum
Abstract: Total sum of all observed values
